{
    "DARV.talk.BILIBILIACGN-BOTTLE_CHARACTER.0-0.char": "你这里……很吵。但东西很多。我在等的时候，顺便看一眼。",
    "DARV.talk.BILIBILIACGN-BOTTLE_CHARACTER.0-0.next": "继续",
    "DARV.talk.BILIBILIACGN-BOTTLE_CHARACTER.0-1.ancient": "那是自然！在这无聊的等待里，随便挑一块被遗忘的宝石去吧！",
    "DARV.talk.BILIBILIACGN-BOTTLE_CHARACTER.1-0r.ancient": "你还在等啊？我不急——那堆东西你慢挑。你等得起，我也等得起！",
    "DARV.talk.BILIBILIACGN-BOTTLE_CHARACTER.2-0.ancient": "我这里有无数宝石，但好像没见着你在等的那件啊……",
    "DARV.talk.BILIBILIACGN-BOTTLE_CHARACTER.2-0.next": "回应",
    "DARV.talk.BILIBILIACGN-BOTTLE_CHARACTER.2-1.char": "若你真有我要的那一件……它不必闪亮。只要它会在该来的时候出现。\n[i][font_size=22]戈多只是站着，像一根被时间磨钝的钉子。[/font_size][/i]",
    "DARV.talk.BILIBILIACGN-BOTTLE_CHARACTER.2-1.next": "继续",
    "DARV.talk.BILIBILIACGN-BOTTLE_CHARACTER.2-2.ancient": "……罢了。把选择留到下次吧。看来你习惯把“下次”等得很久。",
  
    "NEOW.talk.BILIBILIACGN-BOTTLE_CHARACTER.0-0.char": "你又把我从沉默里捞起来……这次，要我去哪里等？",
    "NEOW.talk.BILIBILIACGN-BOTTLE_CHARACTER.0-0.next": "继续",
    "NEOW.talk.BILIBILIACGN-BOTTLE_CHARACTER.0-1.ancient": "[sine]...去... 塔里... ..继续... 等待.....[/sine]",
    "NEOW.talk.BILIBILIACGN-BOTTLE_CHARACTER.1-0r.ancient": "[sine]...我听见了... ..你的脚步..... \n...等待... ..从不赶路.....[/sine]",
    "NEOW.talk.BILIBILIACGN-BOTTLE_CHARACTER.2-0.ancient": "[sine]...你.. 还缺... ..什么...？[/sine]",
    "NEOW.talk.BILIBILIACGN-BOTTLE_CHARACTER.2-0.next": "祈求",
    "NEOW.talk.BILIBILIACGN-BOTTLE_CHARACTER.2-1.char": "若你赐我什么……请赐我“还能再等一次”的力气。别的，我都不缺。",
    "NEOW.talk.BILIBILIACGN-BOTTLE_CHARACTER.2-1.next": "继续",
    "NEOW.talk.BILIBILIACGN-BOTTLE_CHARACTER.2-2.ancient": "[sine]...去吧... \n..我会... 在你...回头的地方... ..还在.....[/sine]",
  
    "OROBAS.talk.BILIBILIACGN-BOTTLE_CHARACTER.0-0.char": "你在跳。我在等。我们谁更疯一点？",
    "OROBAS.talk.BILIBILIACGN-BOTTLE_CHARACTER.0-0.next": "继续",
    "OROBAS.talk.BILIBILIACGN-BOTTLE_CHARACTER.0-1.ancient": "都不疯！！都不疯！！试试这个打发时间！！",
    "OROBAS.talk.BILIBILIACGN-BOTTLE_CHARACTER.1-0r.ancient": "别急别急！你不要急！等待是……是……很长的闪电！！",
    "OROBAS.talk.BILIBILIACGN-BOTTLE_CHARACTER.2-0.ancient": "送你东西！！想要什么？“明天还会响”的声音！？",
    "OROBAS.talk.BILIBILIACGN-BOTTLE_CHARACTER.2-0.next": "回应",
    "OROBAS.talk.BILIBILIACGN-BOTTLE_CHARACTER.2-1.char": "……我把沉默放在口袋里了。你要不要摸摸看？",
    "OROBAS.talk.BILIBILIACGN-BOTTLE_CHARACTER.2-1.next": "继续",
    "OROBAS.talk.BILIBILIACGN-BOTTLE_CHARACTER.2-2.ancient": "好！好！那我们说定了：我继续吵，你继续等！！",
  
    "TANX.talk.BILIBILIACGN-BOTTLE_CHARACTER.0-0.char": "你要战斗。我要等待。我们能不能……各做各的？",
    "TANX.talk.BILIBILIACGN-BOTTLE_CHARACTER.0-0.next": "继续",
    "TANX.talk.BILIBILIACGN-BOTTLE_CHARACTER.0-1.ancient": "[b]不能！！拿着这把武器！去变强！！！[/b]",
    "TANX.talk.BILIBILIACGN-BOTTLE_CHARACTER.1-0r.ancient": "[b]你的血早就凉了！但战斗能让耐心也沸腾起来！！[/b]",
    "TANX.talk.BILIBILIACGN-BOTTLE_CHARACTER.2-0.ancient": "[b]不要再等那个人了！与我一战，这就是你现在的命运！！[/b]",
    "TANX.talk.BILIBILIACGN-BOTTLE_CHARACTER.2-0.next": "退让",
    "TANX.talk.BILIBILIACGN-BOTTLE_CHARACTER.2-1.char": "若一定要打……等我等到那个人来。他会替我还手。\n[i][font_size=22]戈多退半步，像把战场让给未来。[/font_size][/i]",
    "TANX.talk.BILIBILIACGN-BOTTLE_CHARACTER.2-1.next": "继续",
    "TANX.talk.BILIBILIACGN-BOTTLE_CHARACTER.2-2.ancient": "[b]懦弱！！但你有无尽的耐心！！收下这把武器去等待吧！[/b]",
  
    "VAKUU.talk.BILIBILIACGN-BOTTLE_CHARACTER.0-0.char": "恶魔也做交易。那你要我的什么？我的时间？它本来就不值钱。",
    "VAKUU.talk.BILIBILIACGN-BOTTLE_CHARACTER.0-0.next": "继续",
    "VAKUU.talk.BILIBILIACGN-BOTTLE_CHARACTER.0-1.ancient": "不值钱的[sine]时间[/sine]积攒起来，也是很可观的呢……",
    "VAKUU.talk.BILIBILIACGN-BOTTLE_CHARACTER.1-0r.ancient": "我通常把“立刻”卖得很贵。可面对你，我连[sine]“以后”[/sine]都想标上高价。",
    "VAKUU.talk.BILIBILIACGN-BOTTLE_CHARACTER.2-0.ancient": "如果在契约的底端写上一行小字：允许你[sine]永远等下去[/sine]——你就签么？",
    "VAKUU.talk.BILIBILIACGN-BOTTLE_CHARACTER.2-0.next": "回应",
    "VAKUU.talk.BILIBILIACGN-BOTTLE_CHARACTER.2-1.char": "……我的名字不重要。重要的是我还没被叫到。",
    "VAKUU.talk.BILIBILIACGN-BOTTLE_CHARACTER.2-1.next": "继续",
    "VAKUU.talk.BILIBILIACGN-BOTTLE_CHARACTER.2-2.ancient": "拿去你的代价。我绝不会叫醒你——除非[sine]那一刻[/sine]真的来临。",
  
    "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.BILIBILIACGN-BOTTLE_CHARACTER.0-0r.ancient": "你站在这里，却像哪里都不在。你在等什么？塔顶？结局？还是一句许可？",
    "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.BILIBILIACGN-BOTTLE_CHARACTER.0-0r.next": "回答",
    "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.BILIBILIACGN-BOTTLE_CHARACTER.0-1r.char": "……我在等一个名字被念出来。念到之前，我哪儿都不去。",
    "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.BILIBILIACGN-BOTTLE_CHARACTER.0-1r.next": "继续",
    "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.BILIBILIACGN-BOTTLE_CHARACTER.0-2r.ancient": "许可？你从来不需要。你只是害怕“等了却等错”。",
  
    "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.BILIBILIACGN-BOTTLE_CHARACTER.1-0r.ancient": "你又回来。时间对你而言像走廊——你走不完，是因为你不想走完。",
    "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.BILIBILIACGN-BOTTLE_CHARACTER.1-0r.next": "继续",
    "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.BILIBILIACGN-BOTTLE_CHARACTER.1-1r.char": "走廊很好。尽头不好。尽头意味着……不用再等。",
    "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.BILIBILIACGN-BOTTLE_CHARACTER.1-1r.next": "继续",
    "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.BILIBILIACGN-BOTTLE_CHARACTER.1-2r.ancient": "愚蠢。你若不走向尽头，就永远只是回声。",
  
    "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.BILIBILIACGN-BOTTLE_CHARACTER.2-0r.ancient": "那就站着吧。塔会替你记住：你来过，很多次，却什么也没拿走。",
    "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.BILIBILIACGN-BOTTLE_CHARACTER.2-0r.next": "继续",
    "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.BILIBILIACGN-BOTTLE_CHARACTER.2-1r.char": "拿走什么……会让我不等吗？",
    "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.BILIBILIACGN-BOTTLE_CHARACTER.2-1r.next": "继续",
    "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.BILIBILIACGN-BOTTLE_CHARACTER.2-2r.ancient": "会。所以别拿。继续等——这是你唯一擅长的武器。"
  }